itional news media almost completely; they judge that the opportunity cost =
of losing the news audience is not significant. Losing the entire audience =
of YouTube, Facebook, Instagram or TikTok is another matter. Here the dolla=
rs flow, as the opportunity cost of not advertising is usually judged to be=
