ally wanted was to become the owner of an early 2000s forum, like something=
 awful, and have fun messing around with it, everyone paying attention to h=
im as he changes people's avatars and bans people and gets in fights and so=
 on. =E2=80=A6 his current behavior would be completely normal for that kin=
d of thing, it only seems weird here because there's $44 billion at stake.=
=E2=80=9D


