<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Twitter, for Musk, is a place to get in fights=
. He=C2=A0<em>loves=C2=A0</em>getting in fights on Twitter. He would pay an=
y amount of money to do that. He=C2=A0<em>did=C2=A0</em>pay $44 billion to =
do it. (He got a ton of fighting for his money!) He thinks that everyone sh=
ould be happy to pay $8 a month to do it.<a class=3D"footnote-index" href=
