y impression from=C2=A0<em>looking at Twitter </em>is that a lot of people =
love to get in fights and would probably pay $8 a month for it. I probably =
would, and I don=E2=80=99t even like getting in fights on Twitter that much=
; I=E2=80=99d just pay for the optionality. Sometimes you really need to ge=
t in a fight.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">But this is all insane? As a business model ge=
nerally, and as an ad-supported business model in particular? Yesterday Ben=
 Thompson <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/29584608=
.276473/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdHJhdGVjaGVyeS5jb20vMjAyMi9tdXNrcy10d2l0dGVyLWJsdWUtYS1=
