eems incredibly=C2=A0<em>committed=C2=A0</em>to both parts of that.=C2=A0</=
p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">If this comes true, then Musk might have a rea=
lly good time running Twitter? Why not? He=E2=80=99ll run a good message bo=
ard where he can get in fights at all hours of the night, which I think is =
deep down what he really wanted.<a class=3D"footnote-index" href=3D"#footno=
