scope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !im=
portant; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bot=
tom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> I wrote last year</a>,=C2=A0=E2=
=80=9Cbut every stock trade involves an extension of credit.=E2=80=9D Back =
then, I was talking about the deep plumbing of the stock market, plumbing t=
hat broke a little bit in the meme-stock mania and caused Robinhood Markets=
 Inc. to shut down buying of some stocks. But there is a simple retail vers=
ion, too. In general you can open a brokerage account and link your bank ac=
count and transfer $10,000 from your bank account to your brokerage, and th=
at transfer will take <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/cl=
ick/29584608.276473/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2hvcGlmeS5jb20vYmxvZy9ob3ctbG9uZy1kb2V=
zLWFuLWFjaC10cmFuc2Zlci10YWtlIzp-OnRleHQ9QUNIJTIwdHJhbnNmZXJzJTIwYXJlJTIwcH=
